## revfactory-case-015-lsp
- Implemented a dependency-free MiniLang LSP server in `src/server.mjs`.
- Assumptions: MiniLang is line-oriented, `#` comments ignore the rest of a line, and parser recovery should keep collecting symbols after malformed declarations.
